{
  "$comment": [
    "Platform-neutral package list. One entry per tool, with per-platform IDs.",
    "A null ID means 'not applicable / installed another way on that platform'.",
    "`check` is a command name used for a fast idempotency probe before shelling out to the package manager.",
    "",
    "VERIFICATION STATUS: every `winget` ID here has been checked against the live",
    "repository with `winget show --id <id> --exact`. The `brew` and `apt` columns",
    "are UNVERIFIED placeholders to give the macOS/Linux ports a starting shape --",
    "verify each one (`brew info <id>` / `apt-cache show <id>`) before relying on it."
  ],

